comment: Simmons (PHI) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) that does not affect his SQBR and control of the ball.

The shot is imminent when Saric (PHI) is in the paint for about three seconds. 01:37.1 01:37.1
Horford (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Simmons' (PHI) path. Horford's right arm is extended, but the contact with Simmons is marginal.

Embiid (PHI) briefly clamps Horford's (BOS) arm in the post, but the contact does not affect his ability to defend the play.
[Incidental or immaterial] LATR shows that Embiid (PHI) dislodges Rozier (BOS), who is not in position to retrieve the rebound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Celtics possession is confirmed. 01:08.1 01:08.1

Smart (BOS) initiates contact with Saric (PHI) and impedes him in the post.
Saric (PHI) dislodges Smart (BOS) from his legal guarding position in the post.
